serviceRequestOccurrenceSearchParameter

Parameter occurrence:date

Searches for serviceRequest based on to occurrent date eg) /ws/fhir2/{release}/ServiceRequest?occurrence={date}

Expression(none)
Target ResourcesServiceRequest
MultiplesThe parameter cannot repeat or have multiple values
